thread.title_full: Keuken Kampioen Beoordeeld door Mayrin Contreras

author: Mayrin Contreras
title: Mayrin Contreras
text:
Just ordered our new kitchen in Spijkenisse with the great help of Chiong.
We couldn't be happier! He opened the shop 1 hour before for us and helped us with all the doubts and concerns we had. He came out with a great desing for the style we were looking for. We totally felt like VIP customers!
Can't wait to have the new kitchen in our house!!!
